flowchart TD
    Start(["git diff baseRef..HEAD<br/>+ uncommitted + staged"]):::io --> Changed{Any changed<br/>files?}:::core

    Changed -->|no| EmptyGate{runAllIfNoMatches?}:::core
    EmptyGate -->|true| RunAllEmpty[[runAll = true<br/>reason = RUN_ALL_ON_EMPTY_CHANGESET]]:::warn
    EmptyGate -->|false default| Exit0[Exit 0 · skip tests]:::muted

    Changed -->|yes| Mapper{{PathToClassMapper}}:::core

    Mapper -->|".java under sourceDirs"| Prod[Changed production<br/>class FQNs]:::data
    Mapper -->|".java under testDirs"| Direct[Directly changed<br/>test FQNs]:::data
    Mapper -->|matches excludePaths| Excluded[Silently dropped<br/>explicit opt-out]:::muted
    Mapper -->|"non-Java or .java<br/>outside configured dirs"| Unmapped[Unmapped files<br/>yaml · gradle · migrations]:::warn

    Unmapped --> NonJavaGate{runAllOnNonJavaChange?}:::core
    NonJavaGate -->|true default| RunAllNonJava[[runAll = true<br/>reason = RUN_ALL_ON_NON_JAVA_CHANGE]]:::warn
    NonJavaGate -->|false opt-out| Skip[Silent skip<br/>legacy behaviour]:::muted

    Prod --> Engine[[AffectedTestsEngine<br/>4 strategies · merged]]:::core
    Engine --> Naming[naming<br/>Foo → FooTest / FooIT]:::strat
    Engine --> Usage["usage<br/>JavaParser: imports + type refs"]:::strat
    Engine --> Impl[impl<br/>subtypes of changed interfaces]:::strat
    Engine --> Transitive[transitive<br/>reverse-dep walk · N levels]:::strat

    Naming --> Union[Union of affected<br/>test class FQNs]:::data
    Usage --> Union
    Impl --> Union
    Transitive --> Union
    Direct --> Union

    Union --> UnionGate{Union empty?}:::core
    UnionGate -->|no| Router[Group FQNs by<br/>owning Gradle subproject]:::core
    UnionGate -->|yes| DiscoveryEmptyGate{runAllIfNoMatches?}:::core
    DiscoveryEmptyGate -->|true| RunAllDiscovery[[runAll = true<br/>reason = RUN_ALL_IF_NO_MATCHES]]:::warn
    DiscoveryEmptyGate -->|false default| Exit0

    Router --> Dispatch[":moduleA:test --tests FooTest<br/>:moduleB:test --tests BarTest"]:::io

    RunAllEmpty --> FullSuite
    RunAllNonJava --> FullSuite
    RunAllDiscovery --> FullSuite["gradle test<br/>full suite · no --tests filter"]:::io

